          "segments": [
            "1.  It is narrated that Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a.s.) said, “One who speaks  truth,  first  Allah  testifies  to  his  words  and  he considers himself truthful. One who lies, first Allah falsifies his words and that person himself knows that he is a liar.”"
